     <div tabindex="0">
      <div class="slide">
       <img alt="Educational Programs at MHC" height="770" src="/WebGraphicsNew/MHCEducationProgram.jpg" title="Cullowhee Valley" width="1200"/>
       <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="column">
         <div class="container">
          <h2>
           Educational Programs
          </h2>
          <hr/>
          <p>
           The Mountain Heritage Center at WCU is a regional resource for education and research.
                                 We connect people with local history and culture and build bridges between WCU and
                                 the region.
          </p>
          <p>
           The Center works with youth and adult audiences through specially designed gallery,
                                 school, and outreach programs.
          </p>
          <a href="/engage/mountain-heritage-center/educational-programs.aspx">
           Find In-House and Outreach Programs
          </a>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
